race.comment: POP'S MAESTRO (4) is in top form, scoring by 3.5 lengths (25.24) over 457m at this track and making it back to back wins. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in his latest win. Great chance again. GOLDSTAR SANDLER (2) has been out of the placings at his last couple of runs but turned heads when clocking a powerful 25.33 over 457m at this track three starts back. Top win three back and can measure up again. MILES ON IT (1) is having his first try over the longer journey. Missed the frame last time when 8th and beaten 46 lengths (22.68) at Capalaba. Looks one of the chances. CAREER HIGHLIGHT (3) was strongly fancied last time on the back of a win two back but could only manage third (25.57) at this track. Was a winner at his only start from this draw.
